* Zyber came to a dank and dark forest, she weaved around the large trunks of the prehistoric woods. The lilies dangled from her mouth as she sniffed the ground in order to find the plant in which she needed. It was late into the night when she came across the herb that was the main healing source of the mixture...devils club. She looked at the wicked sounding plant and suddenly remembered a poem she had made up the first time she had run into some. Literally!
It went:

Beware the stalks and yellow spines,
prickly as a porcupine.
The devil's club is a plant to fear,
with shiny leaves and wicked spears!

She looked carefully at the plant before her and set the lilies upon the ground, with a silent command she transformed and brought out a small knife.
With a single slash Zyber striped the bush of a few of it's prickly stems, with a near by bit of bark she collected the devil's club and the lilies and began her way to collect the remainder of her herbs.*

_______________________________________________

* Iron Raptor shook her head then ran after Prowl, unarmed. She wanted to know why Plintissa was heading towards the Predacon base without having to shoot her. It puzzled her as to why a bot like Plintissa wished to go to the Pred base, there would be nothing but torture and pain waiting for her no matter what the cause.
Iron Raptor didn't was Plintissa, let alone any bot, to be tortured like that. She called out over her intercom.*

" Plintissa! What in the Matrix are you doing?!"

* Suddenly her scanners alerted her that there was more then just Plintissa ahead, there were two other signatures.( BrightBlade and Gangon) Both Predacon!
Iron Raptor growled as she sped up and took out her splatter gun, she might have to be armed after all!*
